
2021-02-19 Franz Holzinger <franz@ttproducts.de>
    * compatibility TYPO3 10.4: replace $GLOBALS['TSFE']->getUniqueId($formName) by addition of bin2hex(random_bytes(16)) at the end of the form name. This however made a problem. The formname is an id which must be a fix name. So the form name will remain now unchanged.
    * Remove configuration option arrayReturnMode, because only a string must be returned to TYPO3.

